tinymce.Resource.add("tinymce.html-i18n.help-keynav.vi",`<h1>B\u1EAFt \u0111\u1EA7u \u0111i\u1EC1u h\u01B0\u1EDBng b\xE0n ph\xEDm</h1>

<dl>
  <dt>T\u1EADp trung v\xE0o thanh menu</dt>
  <dd>Windows ho\u1EB7c Linux: Alt+F9</dd>
  <dd>macOS: &#x2325;F9</dd>
  <dt>T\u1EADp trung v\xE0o thanh c\xF4ng c\u1EE5</dt>
  <dd>Windows ho\u1EB7c Linux: Alt+F10</dd>
  <dd>macOS: &#x2325;F10</dd>
  <dt>T\u1EADp trung v\xE0o ch\xE2n trang</dt>
  <dd>Windows ho\u1EB7c Linux: Alt+F11</dd>
  <dd>macOS: &#x2325;F11</dd>
  <dt>T\u1EADp trung v\xE0o th\xF4ng b\xE1o</dt>
  <dd>Windows ho\u1EB7c Linux: Alt+F12</dd>
  <dd>macOS: &#x2325;F12</dd>
  <dt>T\u1EADp trung v\xE0o thanh c\xF4ng c\u1EE5 ng\u1EEF c\u1EA3nh</dt>
  <dd>Windows, Linux ho\u1EB7c macOS: Ctrl+F9</dd>
</dl>

<p>\u0110i\u1EC1u h\u01B0\u1EDBng s\u1EBD b\u1EAFt \u0111\u1EA7u t\u1EEB m\u1EE5c UI \u0111\u1EA7u ti\xEAn. M\u1EE5c n\xE0y s\u1EBD \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c t\xF4 s\xE1ng ho\u1EB7c c\xF3 g\u1EA1ch d\u01B0\u1EDBi (n\u1EBFu l\xE0 m\u1EE5c \u0111\u1EA7u ti\xEAn trong
  \u0111\u01B0\u1EDDng d\u1EABn ph\u1EA7n t\u1EED Ch\xE2n trang).</p>

<h1>Di chuy\u1EC3n qua l\u1EA1i gi\u1EEFa c\xE1c ph\u1EA7n UI</h1>

<p>\u0110\u1EC3 di chuy\u1EC3n t\u1EEB m\u1ED9t ph\u1EA7n UI sang ph\u1EA7n ti\u1EBFp theo, \u1EA5n <strong>Tab</strong>.</p>

<p>\u0110\u1EC3 di chuy\u1EC3n t\u1EEB m\u1ED9t ph\u1EA7n UI v\u1EC1 ph\u1EA7n tr\u01B0\u1EDBc \u0111\xF3, \u1EA5n <strong>Shift+Tab</strong>.</p>

<p>Th\u1EE9 t\u1EF1 <strong>Tab</strong> c\u1EE7a c\xE1c ph\u1EA7n UI n\xE0y nh\u01B0 sau:</p>

<ol>
  <li>Thanh menu</li>
  <li>T\u1EEBng nh\xF3m thanh c\xF4ng c\u1EE5</li>
  <li>Thanh b\xEAn</li>
  <li>\u0110\u01B0\u1EDDng d\u1EABn ph\u1EA7n t\u1EED trong ch\xE2n trang</li>
  <li>N\xFAt chuy\u1EC3n \u0111\u1ED5i \u0111\u1EBFm ch\u1EEF \u1EDF ch\xE2n trang</li>
  <li>Li\xEAn k\u1EBFt th\u01B0\u01A1ng hi\u1EC7u \u1EDF ch\xE2n trang</li>
  <li>N\xFAm \u0111i\u1EC1u t\xE1c ch\u1EC9nh k\xEDch c\u1EE1 tr\xECnh so\u1EA1n th\u1EA3o \u1EDF ch\xE2n trang</li>
</ol>

<p>N\u1EBFu ng\u01B0\u1EDDi d\xF9ng kh\xF4ng th\u1EA5y m\u1ED9t ph\u1EA7n UI, th\xEC c\xF3 ngh\u0129a ph\u1EA7n \u0111\xF3 b\u1ECB b\u1ECF qua.</p>

<p>N\u1EBFu \u1EDF ch\xE2n trang c\xF3 t\xEDnh n\u0103ng t\u1EADp trung \u0111i\u1EC1u h\u01B0\u1EDBng b\xE0n ph\xEDm, m\xE0 kh\xF4ng c\xF3 thanh b\xEAn n\xE0o hi\u1EC7n h\u1EEFu, thao t\xE1c \u1EA5n <strong>Shift+Tab</strong>
  s\u1EBD chuy\u1EC3n h\u01B0\u1EDBng t\u1EADp trung v\xE0o nh\xF3m thanh c\xF4ng c\u1EE5 \u0111\u1EA7u ti\xEAn, kh\xF4ng ph\u1EA3i cu\u1ED1i c\xF9ng.</p>

<h1>Di chuy\u1EC3n qua l\u1EA1i trong c\xE1c ph\u1EA7n UI</h1>

<p>\u0110\u1EC3 di chuy\u1EC3n t\u1EEB m\u1ED9t ph\u1EA7n t\u1EED UI sang ph\u1EA7n ti\u1EBFp theo, \u1EA5n ph\xEDm <strong>M\u0169i t\xEAn</strong> t\u01B0\u01A1ng \u1EE9ng cho ph\xF9 h\u1EE3p.</p>

<p>C\xE1c ph\xEDm m\u0169i t\xEAn <strong>Tr\xE1i</strong> v\xE0 <strong>Ph\u1EA3i</strong></p>

<ul>
  <li>di chuy\u1EC3n gi\u1EEFa c\xE1c menu trong thanh menu.</li>
  <li>m\u1EDF menu ph\u1EE5 trong m\u1ED9t menu.</li>
  <li>di chuy\u1EC3n gi\u1EEFa c\xE1c n\xFAt trong nh\xF3m thanh c\xF4ng c\u1EE5.</li>
  <li>di chuy\u1EC3n gi\u1EEFa c\xE1c m\u1EE5c trong \u0111\u01B0\u1EDDng d\u1EABn ph\u1EA7n t\u1EED c\u1EE7a ch\xE2n trang.</li>
</ul>

<p>C\xE1c ph\xEDm m\u0169i t\xEAn <strong>H\u01B0\u1EDBng xu\u1ED1ng</strong> v\xE0 <strong>H\u01B0\u1EDBng l\xEAn</strong></p>

<ul>
  <li>di chuy\u1EC3n gi\u1EEFa c\xE1c m\u1EE5c menu trong menu.</li>
  <li>di chuy\u1EC3n gi\u1EEFa c\xE1c m\u1EE5c trong menu thanh c\xF4ng c\u1EE5 d\u1EA1ng b\u1EADt l\xEAn.</li>
</ul>

<p>C\xE1c ph\xEDm <strong>m\u0169i t\xEAn</strong> xoay v\xF2ng trong m\u1ED9t ph\u1EA7n UI t\u1EADp trung.</p>

<p>\u0110\u1EC3 \u0111\xF3ng m\u1ED9t menu m\u1EDF, m\u1ED9t menu ph\u1EE5 \u0111ang m\u1EDF, ho\u1EB7c m\u1ED9t menu d\u1EA1ng b\u1EADt l\xEAn \u0111ang m\u1EDF, h\xE3y \u1EA5n ph\xEDm <strong>Esc</strong>.</p>

<p>N\u1EBFu tr\u1ECDng t\xE2m hi\u1EC7n t\u1EA1i l\xE0 \u1EDF ph\u1EA7n \u201C\u0111\u1EA7u\u201D c\u1EE7a m\u1ED9t ph\u1EA7n UI c\u1EE5 th\u1EC3, thao t\xE1c \u1EA5n ph\xEDm <strong>Esc</strong> c\u0169ng s\u1EBD tho\xE1t
  to\xE0n b\u1ED9 ph\u1EA7n \u0111i\u1EC1u h\u01B0\u1EDBng b\xE0n ph\xEDm.</p>

<h1>Th\u1EF1c hi\u1EC7n ch\u1EE9c n\u0103ng c\u1EE7a m\u1ED9t m\u1EE5c menu ho\u1EB7c n\xFAt thanh c\xF4ng c\u1EE5</h1>

<p>Khi m\u1EE5c menu ho\u1EB7c n\xFAt thanh c\xF4ng c\u1EE5 mu\u1ED1n d\xF9ng \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c t\xF4 s\xE1ng, h\xE3y \u1EA5n <strong>Return</strong>, <strong>Enter</strong>,
  ho\u1EB7c <strong>Ph\xEDm c\xE1ch</strong> \u0111\u1EC3 th\u1EF1c hi\u1EC7n ch\u1EE9c n\u0103ng m\u1EE5c \u0111\xF3.</p>

<h1>\u0110i\u1EC1u h\u01B0\u1EDBng gi\u1EEFa c\xE1c h\u1ED9p tho\u1EA1i kh\xF4ng c\xF3 nhi\u1EC1u tab</h1>

<p>Trong c\xE1c h\u1ED9p tho\u1EA1i kh\xF4ng c\xF3 nhi\u1EC1u tab, khi h\u1ED9p tho\u1EA1i m\u1EDF ra, tr\u1ECDng t\xE2m s\u1EBD h\u01B0\u1EDBng v\xE0o th\xE0nh ph\u1EA7n t\u01B0\u01A1ng t\xE1c \u0111\u1EA7u ti\xEAn.</p>

<p>Di chuy\u1EC3n gi\u1EEFa c\xE1c th\xE0nh ph\u1EA7n h\u1ED9p tho\u1EA1i t\u01B0\u01A1ng t\xE1c b\u1EB1ng c\xE1ch \u1EA5n <strong>Tab</strong> ho\u1EB7c <strong>Shift+Tab</strong>.</p>

<h1>\u0110i\u1EC1u h\u01B0\u1EDBng gi\u1EEFa c\xE1c h\u1ED9p tho\u1EA1i c\xF3 nhi\u1EC1u tab</h1>

<p>Trong c\xE1c h\u1ED9p tho\u1EA1i c\xF3 nhi\u1EC1u tab, khi h\u1ED9p tho\u1EA1i m\u1EDF ra, tr\u1ECDng t\xE2m s\u1EBD h\u01B0\u1EDBng v\xE0o n\xFAt \u0111\u1EA7u ti\xEAn trong menu tab.</p>

<p>Di chuy\u1EC3n gi\u1EEFa c\xE1c th\xE0nh ph\u1EA7n t\u01B0\u01A1ng t\xE1c c\u1EE7a tab h\u1ED9p tho\u1EA1i n\xE0y b\u1EB1ng c\xE1ch \u1EA5n <strong>Tab</strong> ho\u1EB7c
  <strong>Shift+Tab</strong>.</p>

<p>Chuy\u1EC3n sang m\u1ED9t tab h\u1ED9p tho\u1EA1i kh\xE1c b\u1EB1ng c\xE1ch chuy\u1EC3n tr\u1ECDng t\xE2m v\xE0o menu tab, r\u1ED3i \u1EA5n ph\xEDm <strong>M\u0169i t\xEAn</strong> ph\xF9 h\u1EE3p
  \u0111\u1EC3 xoay v\xF2ng c\xE1c tab hi\u1EC7n c\xF3.</p>
`);
